{"tid":1343122,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港已經返唔到轉頭","createTime":"2019-07-21T18:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T18:42:38.000Z","uid":89627,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3907dce2cf0559ff12f7a99b84f911fa7eb16749","tid":1343122,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:20:03.000Z","msg":"大家唔好被同溫層而影響。香港仲有好多洗曬腦嘅藍絲、廢老喺呢個時刻仲係咁盲撐狗隊。<br />\n<br />\n呢個運動只有兩個結果：一係我地贏，一係我地輸<br />\n唔會再有打和呢回事。<br />\n<br />\n但係有贏輸結果之前，實會有好多場比賽先分到勝負。<br />\n<br />\n過程中香港嘅民生以及樓市等大多實唔會平穩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 簡單啲講=攬炒</span></span><br />\n大家要有定心理準備去應付呢場比賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceeac4d04b914f7cdf684006d565d056112c105c","tid":1343122,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:21:09.000Z","msg":"只有壞與更壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6bafa5a948847936302980f77f05a40dbf127b","tid":1343122,"uid":204352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:21:52.000Z","msg":"最後一戰已經來臨"},{"pid":"72768c3c1e2f6d32922b4c664fc246bf63cd1687","tid":1343122,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:24:05.000Z","msg":"除非今晚警黑合作單嘢可以黎過民意超級一面倒"},{"pid":"45472238109c088701e613897703188a8f3f7ae0","tid":1343122,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:25:41.000Z","msg":"班鄉巴佬係村口停車場學bk d暴徒咁上Gear, 戴晒頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夜麻麻d 白色頭盔點黎既呢<br />\n咁有組織既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d623395acb9b01f68f6f773e2b3bbbb7976227e","tid":1343122,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:26:37.000Z","msg":"兩邊嘅仇意都好大，就算邊一面贏都好。另一面都會反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f54b67215f346c7ce1cd7a7bea1f58280081f1","tid":1343122,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:28:52.000Z","msg":"大家發夢之餘，都要諗吓結局會點。將來結局完咗都可能埋下伏筆，有續集出現"},{"pid":"9e2b491fe63de2844e3b06489419e9f904923ac1","tid":1343122,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:32:39.000Z","msg":"我知大家都預測唔到將來會係點。但大家都要有定心理準備，諗得長遠啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。發夢見到好多細個我嘅人，希望你地有勇有謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a717d5f1d27aec7dfb51fb8ce28ee7912344f5","tid":1343122,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:33:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"247d783067d1a85c69053c1d93c68da03e77050a","tid":1343122,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:35:44.000Z","msg":"今日遊行完全睇到兩代人唔同心態，喺銅鑼灣只叫林鄭下台，一去到中環就光復香港 。"},{"pid":"856b1c5935f5ff211bcf8b37ea54cf78557d015c","tid":1343122,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:35:58.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"1114194cb786b1ccd0d67fb36b1c62c3df7829b1","tid":1343122,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:36:08.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"01fbdbf2957d03ea4d21d9bce12dfb3f0b34aca4","tid":1343122,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:36:26.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"6f93a6beeb3b67a728dd998c471199fd39ebc7b5","tid":1343122,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:37:04.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"39912b7b857121154e91c4374aa64b884fbf7e91","tid":1343122,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:37:25.000Z","msg":"唔需要返轉頭<br />\n長痛不如短痛<br />\n<br />\n我地成全支那"},{"pid":"06e0bdf48a5f44a6c3f764e17bb22a21d8d93bb8","tid":1343122,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39912b7b857121154e91c4374aa64b884fbf7e91","tid":1343122,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim